gāḍha-āliṅgana-saṅgai:-	and by close hearty embraces
tvam-	Thou
aṅganā-lokam-	the women folk
ākulī-cakṛṣe	delighted immensely
By Thy sweet and playful talks, by holding of hands, by the joy of kisses, and by close hearty embraces, Thou delighted the women folk immensely.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:54.000
vāsoharaṇadine yadvāsoharaṇaṃ pratiśrutaṃ tāsām |
tadapi vibho rasavivaśasvāntānāṃ kānta subhruvāmadadhā: ||7||
vāso-haraṇa-dine	on the day when the clothes were stolen
yat-vāso-haraṇam	that stealing of clothes
pratiśrutaṃ tāsām	was promised to them (to the gopis)
tat-api vibho	that also O Lord!
rasa-vivaśa-svāntānāṃ	to bliss overcome minds
